      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Apr 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://gomesfellipe.github.io/projects/appwordcloud/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://gomesfellipe.shinyapps.io/appPCAkmeans/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;low&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;Website&#34;&#xA;    src=&#34;https://img.shields.io/website-up-down-green-red/http/shields.io.svg?label=my-website&amp;amp;style=for-the-badge&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;figure&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;low&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;npm&#34;&#xA;    src=&#34;https://img.shields.io/npm/l/express.svg?style=for-the-badge&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Link do repositório no github: &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/gomesfellipe/appwordcloud&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;https://github.com/gomesfellipe/appwordcloud&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Link de acesso ao app: &lt;a href=&#34;https://gomesfellipe.shinyapps.io/appwordcloud/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;https://gomesfellipe.shinyapps.io/appwordcloud/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;NOVA VERSÃO DA NUVEM DE PALAVRAS!!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Nova versão conta agora com a tabela de frequências dos termos identificados na análise!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;low&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;&#34;&#xA;    src=&#34;https://gomesfellipe.github.io/apps/appwordcloud_files/shiny4.png&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Esta pasta conta com os seguintes arquivos:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Base de dados (obtida através do &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.social-searcher.com/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&